---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@components/sectionhead.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Terms"
  description="Terms for using the JYDream website and contacting JYDream about consulting services, free pilot work, dashboard support, and partner coordination."
>
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">Terms</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        Plain-English website terms for JYDream visitors and prospective
        consulting clients.
      </Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <article class="prose prose-lg mx-auto mt-16 max-w-3xl">
      <p>
        This website is operated by JYDream. By using this website or contacting
        us through the website, you agree to these terms.
      </p>

      <h2>Website information</h2>
      <p>
        The content on this website is provided for general information about
        JYDream's consulting and implementation services. It is not professional
        tax, legal, audit, securities, investment, or accounting advice.
      </p>

      <h2>Professional advice</h2>
      <p>
        JYDream may help clients organize questions and coordinate conversations
        with accountant, tax, legal, audit, securities, or other professional
        partners. Formal advice and sign-off must come from licensed
        professionals.
      </p>

      <h2>Free pilot</h2>
      <p>
        The first two months may be offered as a free pilot for one focused
        workflow. Scope, timing, availability, confidentiality terms, and next
        steps are confirmed directly with each client.
      </p>

      <h2>Confidentiality</h2>
      <p>
        Mutual NDA is available on request. Please do not submit highly
        sensitive information through the website form unless we have agreed on
        a secure intake process.
      </p>

      <h2>External links</h2>
      <p>
        This website may link to client websites or third-party services. Those
        websites are operated by their own owners and may have separate terms
        and privacy policies.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about these terms can be sent to
        <a href="mailto:ted@jydream.ca">ted@jydream.ca</a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </Container>
</Layout>
